Package: ROMOPMappingTools
Title: Tools for Working with OMOP CDM Mappings
Version: 2.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Javier", "Gracia-Tabuenca", , "javier.graciatabuenca@tuni.fi", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2455-0598"))
Description: A comprehensive set of tools for working with mappings in the OMOP Common Data Model (CDM).
    The package provides functions for validating, updating, and managing source-to-concept mappings,
    particularly focusing on the integration with Usagi mapping files and vocabulary management.
